{"id":214224,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":2,"day":5}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"330","ytitle":"","mtitle":"人民的眼睛，雪亮!","ftitle":"","authors":["东方朗"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方朗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的眼睛，雪亮!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切阴谋破坏，休想!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论在黑夜，在自画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万双眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在监视着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特务匪徒的行踪!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在守卫着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民祖国的安全!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无比强大!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁胆敢与人民为敌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁就注定失败!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石早变成釜底游魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦克阿瑟已打得鼻青脸肿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天不会再变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国将永远属于人民!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切特务反革命份子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不趁早向人民投降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更等待何时?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的政府，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽宏大量!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对反革命特务份子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开敞了自新的大门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胁从者可以不问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失足者可以原谅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立功的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还可以得奖!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但对那些罪大恶极"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿悔过自赎的坏蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要镇压!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要惩办!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路只有一条:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非生即死!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切特务反革命份子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果不争取向人民靠拢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新做人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就必然走向灭亡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死路一条!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按:这首诗曾在上海市人民反特广播大会第二天由名电影演员秦怡朗诵。"}]}